%h1 Who are we?
%p
  Lemmata's director is Nigel Lowry.
  Nigel holds computer science degrees from Nottingham and Bristol.
  He started his career on the
  %abbr{title: 'Ministry of Defence'} MOD's
  premier graduate scheme for engineers and scientists, becoming a project manager after two years.
  After this he went back to coding and gained the
  %abbr{title: 'Sun Certified Java Programmer'} SCJP
  and
  %abbr{title: 'Oracle Certified Master Java Developer'} OCMJD
  Java certifications.
  Nigel now works exclusively in Ruby on Rails.
